        <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h3>Subject: Initial Request for Offer Confirmation</h3>
            <p>Hi,</p>
            <p>We are in the process of updating our records. Could you please confirm your offer details at your earliest convenience?</p>
            <p>You can reach us at <a href="mailto:contact@contact.com">Usher</a>.</p>
            <p>By sending the word "confirmation", you will help us ensure that you are willing to take our offer.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your assistance.</p>
            <p>Best regards<br>
            <p>ContactTech HR</p>
        </div>
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">

        <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h3>Re: Initial Request for Email Confirmation</h3>
            <p>Hi,</p>
            <p>Thank you for reaching out. I will confirm the details of offer and get back to you shortly.</p>
            <p>Best regards<br>
        </div>
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">

        <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 30px;">
            <h3>To: Usher (contact@contact.com)</h3>
            <h3>Re: Action Required: Confirmation Email</h3>
            <p>confirmation</p>
        </div>

        <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h3>Subject: Action Required: Confirmation Email</h3>
            <p>Hi,</p>
            <p>I hope this email finds you well.</p>
            <p>We still need your confirmation to proceed with the offer. Could you please confirm your acceptance by replying to this email?</p>
            <p>Kindly send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@contact.com">Usher</a> with the body text:</p>
            <blockquote style="font-style: italic; margin-left: 20px;">confirmation</blockquote>
            <p>This will help us proceed with the next steps. Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
            <p>Best regards<br>
            <p>ContactTech HR</p>
        </div>
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">

